title: Beautiful bright remodeled home in Milpitas Best value
posting_body: ['Gorgeous and fully remodeled Two bedrooms one bath spacious bright, and airy apartment to call home!', 'Best value in Milpitas.', 'Close to freeways (680, 880 and 237), shopping and some of the largest employers in Silicon Valley.', 'The open floor plan of the kitchen, living, and dining areas provide the perfect setting for relaxing or socializing with friends and family after a long day.', '-1 covered parking space', '-New stainless steel appliances (refrigerator, dishwasher, electric stove/oven, Garbage Disposal)', '-Wall Heater', '-New', 'Dual Pane Windows - very quiet and energy efficient', '-Laminate Floors in the living room and bedrooms', '-Tile flooring in kitchen and bathrooms', '-Granite counter-tops, Recessed lighting, High-efficiency LED lighting, Ceiling fan', '-Close to shopping (The Great Mall, Milpitas Town Center), public transport, new bart station.', '-Tenants pay utilities (electric, gas, water) and the owner pays trash, gardener and common utilities..', '-en-suite Laundry and common Laundry on site', 'No Pets, No Smoking.', 'Please call at 650468-3nine66', 'or email for address and schedule an appointment.', 'The showing is by appointment.', 'Open house is on Weekends', 'The monthly rent is $2445.', 'Rent includes Trash Tenants pay PG&E and water.']
